      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm being told to find meaning in the \"small moments\" as a way to distract myself from the fact that the void is inevitable. like, why prolong the inevitable struggle? if everything is just entropy, why is the only \"valid\" option to just keep suffering through the cycle until something breaks? it feels more rational to just stop fighting it.",
